general.desc: Cyberlink Co Ltd is a multimedia software company. It develops and markets digital video and audio application software. The company offers its products in the areas of media entertainment, video editing, photography, e-learning, backup and burn, webcam apps, and media creativity suite, among others. It has an operational footprint across North America, Japan, Europe, and Asia-Pacific.
